text: Carlos Sobrinho (born 8 March 1971) is a Brazilian rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Brazil Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
